<h2>Stay in touch</h2>

<p>We share most days on <a href="https://www.tiktok.com/@prairiecreekadventures" target="_blank" rel="noopener">TikTok</a> and <a href="https://www.instagram.com/prairiecreekadventures" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Instagram</a>. Long-form videos live on <a href="https://www.youtube.com/@adventuresonprairiecreek" target="_blank" rel="noopener">YouTube</a>. And once a week, on Sunday morning, we send a quiet note to anyone who wants it — a paragraph or two from the week, a recipe maybe, a verse, a recommendation. Nothing to buy, nothing to click. Just a letter.</p>

<p>You can <a href="/#subscribe">sign up for that here</a>.</p>

<hr/>

<p>We're so glad you found us. Stay a while.</p>

